Let’s runaway to @hyattmaui 🏝❤️👩🏼‍🤝‍👨🏻

Paradise and Romance, call it a full circle moment because spending the day here together was an absolute dream💕

Our day started off with breakfast at their onsite restaurant Swan Court 🦢where we indulged in their delicious Hawaiian French toast with lilikoi butter and coconut syrup🥞

After having a great breakfast 🍳we headed to check in to our very own private daybed 🏖️overlooking the beautiful golden sandy Kaanapali beach with crystal clear water. Our daybed featured a shade canopy, fresh towels, and our very own server. 

After checking in, we were off to Hyatt’s on-site gorgeous day spa @marilynmonroespas for an amazing couples massage. 💆‍♀️💆‍♂️

After the most amazing spa treatment we headed back to our daybed for some relaxation followed by lunch at Umalu where our server brought us maitais 🍹, our favorite poke nachos, mahi fish tacos 🌮, and fresh poke! 🍣

After lunch, we took in the stunning views, took a swim in the pool, had some Hawaiian shaved ice, and then headed to get ready for @drumsofthepacificluau where we learned more about the legends of Polynesia, watched fire knife dancers, enjoyed a delicious dinner and maybe a maitai or two 😜

Thank you @hyattmaui for having us, we are already dreaming of coming back!🏝️☀️
